movieReviews: Great watch, will watch again, and can recommend.
The Force Awakens, in my opinion at least, is the greatest Star Wars movie.
Though not the best of the Star Wars movies, I still enjoyed it a lot. It was the first Star Wars movie I saw in theaters and it blew me away! Probably my favorite movie experience ever.
